<h2>Terms &amp; Conditions:</h2>
                    <p>Paying for this app will only allow you to add more numbers to your list.</p>
                    <p>If you make a purchase with your airtime, you will keep seeing the adverts on the app. And also we do not track payments made with airtime; so any purchase made with your airtime will be null if you uninstall this app. Re-installing will attract another payment.</p>
                    <p>Payments made from Google Store are recorded and so you will not have to pay again if you are to uninstall the app and re-install.</p>